#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><tip><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:8178
msgid "In <ulink url=\"&thedebianinstaller;\">the debian-installer</ulink> environment, the <literal>udpkg</literal> command is used to open <literal>udeb</literal> packages.  The <literal>udpkg</literal> command is a stripped down version of the <literal>dpkg</literal> command."
