#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:8867
msgid "Create an APT archive key of Foo on your server system as the following."
msgstr "Creare una chiave per l'archivio APT di Pippo nel sistema server, nel modo seguente."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:8868
#, no-wrap
