#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12380
msgid "When your ISP serves you with PPPoE connection and you decide to connect your PC directly to the WAN, the network of your PC must be configured with the PPPoE. The PPPoE stand for PPP over Ethernet. The configuration script <literal>pppoeconf</literal> configures the PPPoE connection interactively."
