msgstr "Vedere \"<literal>/usr/share/doc/wpasupplicant/README.modes.gz</literal>\"."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:12759
msgid "The wireless LAN interface with WEP"
