msgstr "\"start\" se invocato da <literal>ifup</literal>, \"stop\" se invocato da <literal>ifdown</literal>"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><table><tgroup><tbody><row><entry>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:13261
