#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:14633
msgid "Set \"SMTP relay host (blank for none):\" to \"<literal>[smtp.hostname.dom]:587</literal>\" and configure it by the following."
