#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><table><tgroup><tbody><row><entry>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20066
msgid "<literal>sar</literal>(1), <literal>iostat</literal>(1), <literal>mpstat</literal>(1), …: system performance tools for Linux"
msgstr "<literal>sar</literal>(1), <literal>iostat</literal>(1), <literal>mpstat</literal>(1), …: strumenti per le prestazioni di sistema per Linux"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><table><tgroup><tbody><row><entry>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20074
