#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20372
msgid "<literal>find</literal>(1) and <literal>xargs</literal>(1) combination:"
msgstr "Combinazione di <literal>find</literal>(1) e <literal>xargs</literal>(1):"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20376
#, no-wrap
msgid "find . -type f -maxdepth 1 -name '*.ext' -print0 | xargs -0 -n 1 command"
msgstr "find . -type f -maxdepth 1 -name '*.ext' -print0 | xargs -0 -n 1 comando"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20379
msgid "<literal>find</literal>(1) with \"<literal>-exec</literal>\" option with a command:"
msgstr "<literal>find</literal>(1) con l'opzione \"<literal>-exec</literal>\" con un comando:"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20383
#, no-wrap
msgid "find . -type f -maxdepth 1 -name '*.ext' -exec command '{}' \\;"
msgstr "find . -type f -maxdepth 1 -name '*.ext' -exec comando '{}' \\;"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20386
msgid "<literal>find</literal>(1) with \"<literal>-exec</literal>\" option with a short shell script:"
msgstr "<literal>find</literal>(1) con l'opzione \"<literal>-exec</literal>\" con un breve script di shell:"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20390
#, no-wrap
msgid "find . -type f -maxdepth 1 -name '*.ext' -exec sh -c \"command '{}' &amp;&amp; echo 'successful'\" \\;"
msgstr "find . -type f -maxdepth 1 -name '*.ext' -exec sh -c \"comando '{}' &amp;&amp; echo 'esecuzione con successo'\" \\;"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20391
msgid "The above examples are written to ensure proper handling of funny file names such as ones containing spaces.  See <xref linkend=\"_idioms_for_the_selection_of_files\"/> for more advance uses of <literal>find</literal>(1)."
msgstr "Gli esempi precedenti sono stati scritti per assicurare la gestione appropriata di nomi di file particolari come quelli contenenti spazi. Per usi più avanzati di <literal>find</literal>(1), vedere <xref linkend=\"_idioms_for_the_selection_of_files\"/>."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20394
msgid "Starting a program from GUI"
msgstr "Avviare un programma dalla GUI"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20395
msgid "You can set up to start a process from <ulink url=\"&graphicaluserinterfacegui;\">graphical user interface (GUI)</ulink>."
msgstr "È possibile avviare un processo dalla <ulink url=\"&graphicaluserinterfacegui;\">interfaccia utente grafica (GUI)</ulink>."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20396
msgid "Under GNOME desktop environment, a program can be started with proper argument by <emphasis role=\"strong\">double-clicking</emphasis> the launcher icon, by <emphasis role=\"strong\">drag-and-drop</emphasis> of a file icon to the launcher icon, or by \"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Open with …</emphasis>\" menu via right clicking a file icon.  KDE can do the equivalent, too."
msgstr "Nell'ambiente desktop GNOME, un programma può essere avviato con le opzioni appropriate facendo <emphasis role=\"strong\">doppio clic</emphasis> sulla icona del lanciatore, <emphasis role=\"strong\">trascinando e rilasciando</emphasis> un'icona di file sull'icona del lanciatore o usando la voce di menu\"<emphasis role=\"strong\">Apri con …</emphasis>\" che si ottiene cliccando con il pulsante destro sull'icona di un file. Anche in KDE si possono fare le azioni equivalenti."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20397
msgid "Here is an example under GNOME to create a launcher icon for <literal>mc</literal>(1) started in <literal>gnome-terminal</literal>(1)."
msgstr "Quello che segue è un esempio per GNOME di creazione di un'icona di lanciatore per <literal>mc</literal>(1) avviato in <literal>gnome-terminal</literal>(1)."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20398
msgid "Create an executable program \"<literal>mc-term</literal>\" by the following."
msgstr "Creare un programma \"<literal>mc-term</literal>\" eseguibile nel modo seguente."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><screen>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20399
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"# cat &gt;/usr/local/bin/mc-term &lt;&lt;EOF\n"
"#!/bin/sh\n"
"gnome-terminal -e \"mc \\$1\"\n"
"EOF\n"
"# chmod 755 /usr/local/bin/mc-term"
msgstr ""
"# cat &gt;/usr/local/bin/mc-term &lt;&lt;EOF\n"
"#!/bin/sh\n"
"gnome-terminal -e \"mc \\$1\"\n"
"EOF\n"
"# chmod 755 /usr/local/bin/mc-term"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20404
msgid "Create a desktop launcher as the following."
msgstr "Creare un lanciatore sul desktop nel modo seguente."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20408
msgid "Right click desktop space to select \"<literal>Create Launcher …</literal>\"."
msgstr "Cliccare col pulsante destro in uno spazio libero sul desktop e selezionare \"<literal>Crea lanciatore…</literal>\"."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20413
msgid "Set \"Type\" to \"<literal>Application</literal>\"."
msgstr "Impostare \"Tipo\" ad \"<literal>Applicazione</literal>\"."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20418
msgid "Set \"Name\" to \"<literal>mc</literal>\"."
msgstr "Impostare \"Nome\" a \"<literal>mc</literal>\"."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20423
msgid "Set \"Command\" to \"<literal>mc-term %f</literal>\"."
msgstr "Impostare \"Comando\" a \"<literal>mc-term %f</literal>\"."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20428
msgid "Click \"OK\"."
msgstr "Fare clic su \"OK\"."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20432
