#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><itemizedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:20496
msgid "the \"<literal>~/.mailcap</literal>\" and \"<literal>/etc/mailcap</literal>\" file contents which associate <ulink url=\"&mime;\">MIME</ulink> type with program (see <literal>mailcap</literal>(5))"
