msgstr "Creare \"<literal>/usr/sbin/policy-rc.d</literal>\" che restituisca sempre il codice 101"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><orderedlist><listitem><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:22151
msgid "Run \"<literal>chroot /sid-root bin/bash -c 'exec -a -bash bin/bash'</literal>\""
msgstr "Esegiore \"<literal>chroot /sid-root bin/bash -c 'exec -a -bash bin/bash'</literal>\""

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><note><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:22156
msgid "Some programs under chroot may require access to more files from the parent system to function than <literal>pbuilder</literal> provides.  For example, \"<literal>/sys</literal>\", \"<literal>/etc/passwd</literal>\", \"<literal>/etc/group</literal>\", \"<literal>/var/run/utmp</literal>\", \"<literal>/var/log/wtmp</literal>\", etc. may need to be bind-mounted or copied."
msgstr "Alcuni programmi in chroot per funzionare possono aver bisogno dell'accesso ad più file nel sistema genitore di quanti ne fornisca <literal>pbuilder</literal>. Per esempio, per essere montati con bind o copiati, possono essere necessari \"<literal>/sys</literal>\", \"<literal>/etc/passwd</literal>\", \"<literal>/etc/group</literal>\", \"<literal>/var/run/utmp</literal>\", \"<literal>/var/log/wtmp</literal>\", ecc."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><note><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:22159
msgid "The \"<literal>/usr/sbin/policy-rc.d</literal>\" file prevents daemon programs to be started automatically on Debian system.  See \"<literal>/usr/share/doc/sysv-rc/README.policy-rc.d.gz</literal>\"."
msgstr "Il file \"<literal>/usr/sbin/policy-rc.d</literal>\" evita che, in un sistema Debian, i programmi demone vengano avviati automaticamente. Vedere \"<literal>/usr/share/doc/sysv-rc/README.policy-rc.d.gz</literal>\"."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><tip><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:22162
msgid "The original purpose of the specialized chroot package, <literal>pbuilder</literal> is to construct a chroot system and builds a package inside the chroot.  It is an ideal system to use to check that a package's build-dependencies are correct, and to be sure that unnecessary and wrong build dependencies do not exist in the resulting package."
msgstr "Lo scopo originale del pacchetto specializzato chroot, <literal>pbuilder</literal> è di costruire un sistema chroot e di compilare un pacchetto all'interno del chroot. È un sistema ideale per controllare che le dipendenze di compilazione di un pacchetto siano corrette e per assicurare che, nel pacchetto risultante, non ci siano dipendenze sbagliate o superflue."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><tip><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:22165
msgid "Similar <literal>schroot</literal> package may give you an idea to run <literal>i386</literal> chroot system under <literal>amd64</literal> parent system."
msgstr "Il pacchetto simile <literal>schroot</literal> può dare un'idea di come eseguire un sistema chroot <literal>i386</literal> in un sistema genitore <literal>amd64</literal>."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><title>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:22169
msgid "Multiple desktop systems"
msgstr "Sistemi desktop multipli"

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:22170
msgid "I recommend you to use <ulink url=\"&qemu;\">QEMU</ulink> or <ulink url=\"&virtualbox;\">VirtualBox</ulink> on a Debian <literal>stable</literal> system to run multiple desktop systems safely using <ulink url=\"&virtualization;\">virtualization</ulink>.  These enable you to run desktop applications of Debian <literal>unstable</literal> and <literal>testing</literal> without usual risks associated with them."
msgstr "Io raccomando l'uso di <ulink url=\"&qemu;\">QEMU</ulink> o <ulink url=\"&virtualbox;\">VirtualBox</ulink> per eseguire, in un sistema Debian <literal>stable</literal>, sistemi desktop multipli in maniera sicura usando la <ulink url=\"&virtualization;\">virtualizzazione</ulink>. Permettono di eseguire applicazioni desktop di Debian <literal>unstable</literal> e <literal>testing</literal> senza i comuni rischi ad essi associati."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:22171
msgid "Since pure <ulink url=\"&qemu;\">QEMU</ulink> is very slow, it is recommended to accelerate it with <ulink url=\"&kvm;\">KVM</ulink> when the host system support it."
msgstr "Dato che <ulink url=\"&qemu;\">QEMU</ulink> puro è molto lento, è raccomandata la sua velocizzazione con <ulink url=\"&kvm;\">KVM</ulink> quando il sistema host lo permette."

#. type: Content of: <book><chapter><section><section><simpara>
#: debian-reference.en.xmlt:22172
msgid "The virtual disk image \"<literal>virtdisk.qcow2</literal>\" containing Debian system for <ulink url=\"&qemu;\">QEMU</ulink> can be created using <ulink url=\"&debianinstallersmallcds;\">debian-installer: Small CDs</ulink> as follows."
msgstr "L'immagine disco virtuale \"<literal>virtdisk.qcow2</literal>\" contenente il sistema Debian per <ulink url=\"&qemu;\">QEMU</ulink> si può creare con i<ulink url=\"&debianinstallersmallcds;\">piccoli CD dell'installatore Debian</ulink> nel modo seguente."

