msgid "The <ulink url=\"&texlive;\">TeX Live</ulink> software distribution offers a complete TeX system.  The <literal>texlive</literal> metapackage provides a decent selection of the <ulink url=\"&texlive;\">TeX Live</ulink> packages which should suffice for the most common tasks."
