msgid "When documents become bigger, sometimes TeX may cause errors.  You must increase pool size in \"<literal>/etc/texmf/texmf.cnf</literal>\" (or more appropriately edit \"<literal>/etc/texmf/texmf.d/95NonPath</literal>\" and run <literal>update-texmf</literal>(8)) to fix this."
